  "body": "# Expanded Mace Enchantings\n\n**This Datapack and Mod** expands the Mace's enchantments so that it has the Sword's enchantments.\n\n**‎◾Example:**\n\n![Expanded Mace Enchantings](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8784ab678db56fb92cab7fb9996770b5328deb95.jpeg)\n\n\n## Details📝\n\n- **Expanded Mace Enchantings** is **compatible** with versions **1.21 to 1.21.11**\n- **Expanded Mace Enchantings** adds new  **(expansion)** to enchanting table🌐\n- **Expanded Mace Enchantings** is compatible with any **enchantings datapacks**\n- **No** it is necessary to **unzip** the downloaded file 🗂️\n\n## More Projects:\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/datapack/expanded-armor-enchantings\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/TM5K3dNM/ezgif-com-speed-43.gif\" alt=\"ezgif com speed (43)\" border=\"0\"></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/expanded-weapon-enchantings\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/bML9W70B/ezgif-com-speed-44.gif\" alt=\"ezgif com speed (44)\" border=\"0\"></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/datapack/expanded-trident-enchantings\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/VcwSJqRJ/Expanded-Trident-Enchants-Logo.jpg\" alt=\"Expanded Trident Enchants Logo\" border=\"0\"></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/datapack/expanded-mace-enchantings\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/LXv2pS15/Expanded-Mace-Enchants-Logo-2.jpg\" alt=\"Expanded Mace Enchants Logo (2)\" border=\"0\"></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/datapack/expanded-axe-enchantings\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/Fqxsn0qL/ezgif-com-speed-47.gif\" alt=\"ezgif com speed (47)\" border=\"0\"></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/datapack/expanded-bow-enchantings\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/VWLkm7bC/ezgif-com-speed-48.gif\" alt=\"ezgif com speed (48)\" border=\"0\"></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/datapack/expanded-crossbow-enchantings\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/PzT0xXgD/ezgif-com-speed-49.gif\" alt=\"ezgif com speed (49)\" border=\"0\"></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/datapack/expanded-spear-enchantings\"><img sr